2️⃣ JS Changes

Add this to your Index.cshtml inside <script> section:

// Override openEstimatePopup to enforce Vehicle tab first and disable others
function openEstimatePopup(vehicleId) {
    var popup = $("#vehPopupWindow").data("kendoWindow");
    popup.center().open();

    // Activate vehicle tab only, disable others
    var tabstrip = $("#estimateTabs").data("kendoTabStrip");
    tabstrip.activateTab(tabstrip.tabGroup.children().eq(0)); // Vehicle tab
    tabstrip.tabGroup.children().addClass("k-state-disabled"); 
    tabstrip.tabGroup.children().eq(0).removeClass("k-state-disabled"); 

    // Load data if edit
    if (vehicleId) {
        // existing logic for edit
    }
}

// After save success, enable all tabs
function enableAllTabs() {
    var tabstrip = $("#estimateTabs").data("kendoTabStrip");
    tabstrip.tabGroup.children().removeClass("k-state-disabled");
}

// Stub: Add new record
function addNewRecord() {
    alert("Stub: Add New Record function called. Implement later.");
}


Call enableAllTabs() at the end of your save success logic.

3️⃣ Index.cshtml (only changes)

Add CSS reference:

<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/custom-ui.css" />


Wrap your vehicle estimate header with:

<h6 class="vehicle-estimate-header">Vehicle Estimate</h6>


Ensure your tabstrip has id="estimateTabs":

@(Html.Kendo().TabStrip()
      .Name("estimateTabs")
      ...
)

4️⃣ _VehPopUp.cshtml

Keep wrapper id="vehPopupForm".

Remove inline styles from form groups/labels/inputs (CSS takes over).

Buttons should have class="btn" (they’ll get styled automatically).

Example change:

<div id="vehPopupForm">
    <div class="form-group">
        @Html.LabelFor(m => m.VehicleListId, "Estimate #", new { @class = "form-label" })
        @(Html.Kendo().TextBoxFor(m => m.VehicleListId).HtmlAttributes(new { @class = "form-control" }))
    </div>
    <div class="mt-3">
        <button id="btnSaveScPart" class="btn">Save</button>
        <button id="btnCancelScPart" class="btn">Cancel</button>
    </div>
</div>

5️⃣ TotalCost.cshtml

Same cleanup as _VehPopUp.cshtml.

Ensure controls have .form-control.

Ensure form groups use .form-group & .form-label.

No inline styles.
